data.title: Tigers Finish 10th at Rose
data.meta_description: Stories, updates and press releases from DePauw University.
data.text:
Tigers Finish 10th at Rose-Hulman Twilight

April 17, 2010

April 16, 2010, Terre Haute, Ind. â€” DePauw totaled 23 points and finished 10th at the Rose-Hulman Twilight Meet. Vincennes won with 133.5 points, while Marian was second with 102.5.

Nick Pucillo finished third in the steeplechase in 9:39.05 as did Chris Dietrick in the 1,500 meters in 3:59.08. Joe Evans placed fifth in the 1,500 meters in 3:59.82, while Robert Steele was third in the 400 meters in 49.98 seconds and Max Bush was eighth in the 3,000 meters in 9:20.29.

DePauw returns to action on Friday, April 23, at the Southern Collegiate Athletic Conference Championships at Hendrix College.
